Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.41,0:00:06.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Manatsu-kun will be staying in the \Nhospital for a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:09.44,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:11.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You hit your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You still have more tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.19,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You should have them check you out thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.53,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Pitz says so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:23.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You know animals aren't allowed \Nin the medical center...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:26.79,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akari taught me a magic spell to \Nmake you feel better, Daichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:28.79,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:31.78,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, don't, don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.78,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Belly Button Forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:35.11,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't do that! Hide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:36.85,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Restraint! Restraint!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:39.18,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You don't feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.76,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,No... When you're wearing a dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:44.76,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Belly Button Forte is more of an \Noffensive spell than a healing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:54.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:57.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:04.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei, Commander Nishikubo \Nwants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:05.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:08.92,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can all live together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.87,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,And make dinner and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.29,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:17.47,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a little while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:20.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems like the distant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:24.50,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it feels so far away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:29.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.15,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something bad to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:44.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I found out who I really am,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.33,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,something I had wondered for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:52.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know the Machine Goodfellows \Noperated off of Orgone energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:53.67,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Pitz told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:56.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you think I might be your enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:58.80,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:03.39,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you would save Daichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I return to the Kiltgang,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:09.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I might turn into a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:13.48,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:16.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have so much faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:19.07,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.63,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Speed is of the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.92,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Registration code 10878F.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:05.21,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the members selected \Nto participate in the Kivotos Plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:08.01,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,currently in cold sleep in \Nthe {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}'s Ark block.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:12.00,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,They are attempting to capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.48,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:17.08,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided you are appropriate for this mission
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.69,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,due to your combat training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.49,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.97,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,He is a prisoner undergoing sentencing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.11,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,for assault and attempted murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:28.37,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,A prisoner is a Kivotos Plan member?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:29.95,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.75,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,His genes appear to have been \Nthe reason for his selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.90,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Eiji Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:37.84,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,"Arashi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.58,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who gave you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.30,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,a designer child, your genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.98,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,You might say he's your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:53.02,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is this mission being undertaken in \Nconjunction with the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:57.31,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,That should mean there's no \Nneed for me to go to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:02.84,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided not to give headquarters the \Ninformation about you and the Kiltgang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.30,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what that means, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:12.41,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's a top secret mission, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.91,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Starry Sky's Picture Book
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is the {\i1}Red Papillon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I will reach the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0} in fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tanegashima. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.77,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's okay for \NAkari-chan to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.35,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dangerous mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:42.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Getting permission to capture one of the \NKivotos Plan sleepers would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.35,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Especially with a commander
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.82,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,who belongs to the Intercept Faction, \Nwhich opposes the Ark Faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:51.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,If they're going to resort to \Nviolent, illegal measures,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:54.27,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to take the initiative and capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:58.25,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,And for that, we need a reason to \Nsend Teppei to the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:03.13,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,So you invented a reason about \NAkari-chan wanting to see her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.09,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:09.09,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed she didn't get mad, \Nbeing used for a mission like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,She thought it was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:20.80,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she really did want to see her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.53,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's her daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.59,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't they going after Eiji Arashi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.02,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,because after the last battle, they began to suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.49,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,the relationship between Teppei and the Kiltgang?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:39.27,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei is quarantined at this base, \Nso they can't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:43.16,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're going after \Nhis gene donor, Eiji, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:46.76,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,And we're sending Teppei \Nstraight into the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:49.71,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,And that isn't logical at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.51,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:54.30,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You have a plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:07:00.41,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at this point, we're all in this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.35,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red Papillon{\i0} is about to rendezvous \Nwith the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:30.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:47.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How rich do you have to be to travel \Ninto orbit just to see your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Governor Yomatsuri hasn't been \Ndown to the surface in years...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They probably made an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You've really grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.28,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:01.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy that you said \Nyou wanted to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.11,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.21,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This seems kind of strange to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:14.07,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That young pilot is kind of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:14.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we'll have some time to talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:23.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there was another shuttle at the dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.07,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's the regular supply shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Regular?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There are twenty-five containers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We've brought them all aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Container loading confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:46.37,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Time for work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.59,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to talk to your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.08,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This seems more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to use this, you need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:11.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The corridor to the Kivotos Plan cold sleep \Nblock, also known as the Ark block,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:14.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,is protected by dozens of bulkheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:17.93,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,On the outside, it's a long-distance \Nspaceflight staffed by volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:23.04,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality, it's a secret plan for \Ncarefully chosen elites to escape Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:27.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If this got out, there could be panic and rioting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:32.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, my mom's requested that \NI be in the third group of sleepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:36.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Ark Faction thinks anyone who \Nstays on Earth will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're too pessimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.10,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely with the Intercept Faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:42.79,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:47.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Some of this sector's alarms have been shut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else sneaked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:55.78,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I think spies sneaked in from \Nthe supply shuttle at the dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:10:00.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm here, we have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:03.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Logical, logical... Open sesame!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:06.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:12.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how much do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Akari, Teppei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:18.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you know \Nabout this mission, Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.82,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If you mean that the target was your gene donor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.56,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,they didn't tell me, but I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You learned it all through hacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.52,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.93,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:34.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly wanted to meet this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:44.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Number 10801F to number 10900F.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:45.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:55.59,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:58.71,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Number 10878F.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:10:59.84,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm unloading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.60,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This man is my gene donor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:16.25,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He looks more like a boy than a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.11,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They've entered the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.85,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That was faster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be here before we can wake him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:29.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this sector have emergency blast doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.04,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:33.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Can you close them without triggering the alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.73,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.61,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,For normal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to the magical girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:46.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use the time to wake him, and take him \Nthrough the emergency hatch in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:13.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:20.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is not part of the \Noriginal Kivotos Plan program.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:25.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You've been awakened early for another reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.70,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,You're Teppei, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.52,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.97,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell with one look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.57,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, you've grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They'll unlock the door soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.65,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the target?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.70,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be a good hacker, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a line in, and I can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm a magical girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.25,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:46.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The target's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like someone got here before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there was a \NTanegashima shuttle here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:09.13,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that'll get them off our trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:11.41,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you came up with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.37,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:21.96,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.02,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, she isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:49.60,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,At your age, your mom and \Ndad were already in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,My "dad"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.30,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:06.71,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,What is a "dad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:10.92,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.45,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,An ambush, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.47,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Just one, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:19.86,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.02,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is a tranquilizer gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.18,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:27.19,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we'll use that... and these.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:36.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Empty spacesuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:01.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.54,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:25.10,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,There's a high probability that \Nthey know where we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.84,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Staying here is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:30.02,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for spacesuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're going outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.41,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The external hatches aren't \Nelectronically controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.98,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You need a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:38.81,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.84,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Plastic explosives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:44.77,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,We can use it to go outside, reach \Nthe dock, and steal their shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.68,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But we have our own shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.82,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Given the nature of their operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.79,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,their shuttle will be ready to \Nleave at a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.70,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Stealing it will be faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:58.78,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,With your magic, we can take over \Ntheir navigation system, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.58,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Do as your dad says.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:27.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble with bulkhead 1883.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:27.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.68,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.50,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's their shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:58.14,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Teppei, your dad—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Would you stop calling yourself that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:06.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you may think,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:10.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't see you that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And it isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not who you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.75,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:43.01,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even get to read you a single picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.02,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I really regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:54.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,My tranquilizer gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:58.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:00.81,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.44,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we stealing the shuttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:06.19,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:07.98,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:12.20,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,That shot wounded me worse than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.56,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I can't protect you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.47,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,They're pros...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:19.35,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell they're a lot like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:25.26,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,But they're after me, so if I \Nsurrender, you'll both be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.73,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if they're after my genes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.34,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,their real target would be Teppei, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:36.69,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why Teppei was sent here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:40.81,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe someone wanted him to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:44.44,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'm sure it was \Nsomething the adults wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:50.00,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,But if a girl like you is with him, \NI don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.31,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei's dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.42,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I like the way that sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.50,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.78,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:14.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,His assault and attempted murder \Nwere both to protect Teppei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:17.86,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to stop Teppei, his child,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:22.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,from being used as a test subject \Nby Macbeth Enterprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:30.50,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Was having Teppei meet him your true goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:34.07,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:54.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This was Commander Nishikubo's order?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:58.53,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I lied to you for the sake of the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:00.86,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever your reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:07.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can't imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,how happy I was to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When she looks at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:33.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Governor Yomatsuri seems so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:40.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That was a weird thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:48.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He looked at you the same way \Nthat my mom looks at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:57.58,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the group that kidnapped the \Ntarget was under Salty Dog's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:00.58,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They've denied it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:02.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The mission was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:08.38,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:12.89,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Once the shuttle arrived, Eiji Arashi escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.98,0:22:15.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,His whereabouts are currently unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:18.65,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:21.16,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:27.28,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:33.03,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even get to read you a single picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:43.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,My dad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:19.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Kivotos Plan was proposed as the \Nlast hope for the survival of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.40,0:24:23.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But many conspiracies lurk in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.99,0:24:25.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And Hirosue, from Salty Dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.38,0:24:29.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,tries to kidnap Hana for the Kivotos Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:32.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 6 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:34.82,Title2,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kivotos Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.13,0:24:34.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kivotos Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.82,0:24:37.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, expand!
